something more snappy.

Suggested-by: Tvrtko Ursulin <tvrtko.ursulin@linux.intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Matthew Auld <matthew.auld@intel.com>
Reviewed-by: Thomas Hellstr√∂m <thomas.hellstrom@linux.intel.com>
